About this content

May 02, 2012

Keep up to date with all the latest Canadian Product Recall, Warning, and Advisory 
information issued by Health Canada that can affect you and your loved one lives.  
If it is not safe for a Canadian, chances are it is not safe for you!  

Canuck Product Safety is not affiliated with Health Canada or any other Canadian Governmental 
Agency. All the advisory, warnings and recalls content can be found directly on Health Canada's 
website http://hc-sc.gc.ca. This application is designed to provide Windows Phone specific experience 
for accessing Product Recall, Warning, and Advisory information issued by Health Canada.

